{"tid":1413994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[細思極恐] 獨立調查委員會","createTime":"2019-08-05T11:27:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T12:20:08.000Z","uid":103983,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e0a28f95f1dd1060f13aaea0cf386b5845c72df5","tid":1413994,"uid":103983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:27:10.000Z","msg":"琴晚瞓覺一直諗<br />\n<br />\n點解中共一邊撐警 ?<br />\n一邊又推獨立調查?<br />\n<br />\n又點解罷工前先出記招?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n終於俾我諗到答案<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一 拖時間</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共最興玩滲透<br />\n叫班高官龜縮拖時間<br />\n睇住你班友仔同狗打下交 <br />\n打得愈勁愈好<br />\n暴力升級就最好<br />\n<br />\n 一黎 和理非會反感<br />\n二黎  有時間去滲透連登網媒<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但係 罷工佢就驚啦</span><br />\n<br />\n睇下今日即刻出黎講野 開晒記招 <br />\n央視 韓國瑜都發聲<br />\n<br />\n背後班商家佬俾壓力<br />\n証明罷工係有用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">二 斬斷警察退路</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n試諗下<br />\n打輸左 邊個夠膽唔撈 <br />\n都會被秋後算帳 <br />\n列入調查名單<br />\n<br />\n呢個係逼警察站隊<br />\n用黎團結警隊嘅心理策略<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打住咁多先<br />\n大家可以集思廣益<br />\n諗下點拆局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"106bd6ac58912575e88213e7214ae47bfdda5d04","tid":1413994,"uid":103983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:28:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c92f6500518fcc346808f4da74f2a43ae27a8c","tid":1413994,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:34:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">200%令政府中央收皮(和平合法易過長期罷工)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1412496\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1412496</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span>"},{"pid":"6e82d8c2a7f1c12628839c3302a6c0c43c5c186b","tid":1413994,"uid":103983,"like":0,"disli